{"tid":2067323,"cid":13,"subCid":0,"title":"MADNESS 搖身一變成日牌??","createTime":"2020-06-17T02:19:07.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-18T09:14:08.000Z","uid":258546,"like":0,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"839d4b98a94e9e335832813c130a10b6ff5e672a","tid":2067323,"uid":258546,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-17T02:19:07.000Z","msg":"日本潮流名所 STUDIOUS TOKYO 以東京為名，堅持嚴選日本製造的原創品牌，就連 L.DOPE 介紹過的不少獨立設計師品牌它們也有引進。近年開始進軍中國市場的 STUDIOUS 陸續開設香港及上海門市，本月又將展開最新的深圳分店。<br />\n<br />\n為慶祝深圳門店開業，STUDIOUS 與 MADNESS 共同打造了全新支線 &ldquo;MADNESS TOKYO&ldquo;，並邀請以解構拼貼技法著稱的藝術家河村康輔（Kosuke Kawamura）設計了一系列「日本製」的 T 恤，主題涵蓋 Forest、Skull、Collage、City 及 Money 等五種圖像，其中除了河村康輔過往的經典創作，其中 Skull 更是以余文樂飼養的小狗為主角的全新作品。<br />\n<br />\nMADNESS TOKYO &times; Kosuke Kawamura 系列商品將於 6 月 20 日在全新開幕的 STUDIOUS 深圳店先行販售，並在 6 月 26 日上架 STUDIOUS 上海、香港及東京神南店，往後的 MADNESS TOKYO 商品也將由 STUDIOUS 獨家販賣！<br />\n<a href=\"https://ldope.com/news/fashion/apparel/studious-madness-tokyo-kosuke-kawamura-shenzhen/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fldope.com%2Fnews%2Ffashion%2Fapparel%2Fstudious-madness-tokyo-kosuke-kawamura-shenzhen%2F&d=3WJ6yD1ie6zkJWt%2B9GiXG1YPZSwMlx1ag7qd%2FaAfmLs%3D&h=579b5566\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://ldope.com/news/fashion/apparel/studious-madness-tokyo-kosuke-kawamura-shenzhen/</a><br />\n<br />\nSucks......<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"396622110f4fbc820ffc3ef684227ff2f47e9a75","tid":2067323,"uid":7823,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-1